Now what can they say against it, pray, if, being neither unacquainted with the medical art, nor un­ skilled in it, I seek for certain antidotes in fishes ?
for as very many such are mingled and implanted in all other ob­ jects by the bounty of nature, so too there are some, no doubt, to be found in fishes.
